allas-conf project_2009316
## Note: it takes a moment or two

## From the scratch folder where data is stored, run the code below to uploads data
a-put FILE -b YOUR_RAW_DATA_BUCKET
## "-b" specifies a "bucket", a folder in which the data is stored and then the name of this

